%h3 Sign in to THISYEARI.com using your account with one of the following providers.
%p.lead
  After clicking an icon below, you will be redirected back to this website.


.row
  .col-md-3
    = link_to "#{content_tag(:h2, 'Google')}#{icon('google-plus')}".html_safe, user_omniauth_authorize_path(provider: :google_oauth2), class: 'xxl'
  .col-md-3
    = link_to "#{content_tag(:h2, 'Twitter')}#{icon('twitter')}".html_safe, user_omniauth_authorize_path(provider: :twitter), class: 'xxl'
  .col-md-3
    = link_to "#{content_tag(:h2, 'Facebook')}#{icon('facebook')}".html_safe, user_omniauth_authorize_path(provider: :facebook), class: 'xxl'

%p.lead
  Don't worry. We won't post on your wall or on your timeline or share your info with anyone or annoy you.
